# Second Brain Vault

This vault is maintained by the Second Brain skill pack.

- `inbox/`: raw source files.
- `inbox/index.md`: AI-maintained source table of contents.
- `compiled/concepts/`: factual synthesis pages.
- `compiled/opinions/`: user-view and thesis pages.
- `compiled/questions.md`: append-only open questions.
- `compiled/digests/`: periodic synthesis pages.
- `.second-brain.yml`: folder, frontmatter, link, and behavior config.
- `style.md`: user-editable writing and research behavior. Commands read this before acting.
- `log.md`: append-only audit trail.
